Project Description
The "Telerik MVC Controls : Extended Client API" extends the Telerik client-side API to provide a rich client API for the Telerik MVC controls.

This project is NOT affiliated with the telerik and is therefore NOT supported by telerik. Please direct all questions/concerns/requests about the Telerik Extensions For ASP.NET MVC : Extended Client API on the Discussions tab.
